verbose_text: Interestingly, RNAi mediated knockdown of edc-3 did not cause significant modification of the life expectancy of dcap-2 mutants, while dcap-2 knockdown significantly reduced the lifespan of edc-3 mutants (XREF_SUPPLEMENTARY C; XREF_SUPPLEMENTARY).
evidence: edc-3 did not cause significant modification of the life expectancy of dcap-2 mutants
